Readme
------

This module enables teams to track outstanding items which need resolution. It provides e-mail notifications to
members about updates to items. Similar to many issue tracking systems.
Send comments to kjartan@drupal.org.

Requirements
------------

This module requires the lastest version of the current Drupal CVS version.

Installation
------------

1. Create the SQL tables. This depends a little on your system, but the most
   common method is:
     mysql -u username -ppassword drupal < project.mysql

2. Copy the project.module to the Drupal modules/ directory.

3. Enable the module under "site configuration"

4. Use the administration pages to setup projects.

Author
